annotationA: 60S ribosomal export protein NMD3; Acts as an adapter for the XPO1/CRM1-mediated export of the 60S ribosomal subunit
annotationB: 60S ribosomal protein L23; Structural constituent of ribosome; myosin binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization; neurogenesis; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL14 family
